<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext">{{Infobox mapframe |id=Q1318331 |length_mi=3.5}}</syntaxhighlight>
{{Infobox mapframe |id=Q1318331 |length_km=5.6}}
Determine zoom from object area in square kilometres or square miles
